{ White has already moved the bishop three times, and after ...Bg5 is forced to move it again, losing important developing tempi. }
15. Qa7 Bxd2+ 16. Kxd2 Bf5
{ Black has a great position thanks to all the developed pieces and unstable king on d2. }
