{ White's castle is destroyed, and Black already has a superior position. } 17.
Qf2 Qe7+
{ As we said before, trading pieces generally favors White. So It's better to avoid exchanging queens. }
18. Be2 Ne5
{ Even if White can still castle, Black has excellent prospects of attack thanks to the piece coordination. }
