19... Qh4 20. h3 f5 { Trying to open the f-file against the white king. } 21.
gxf5 Bxa2 { Without any fear. The bishop cannot be trapped. } 22. O-O Rcd8
{ It is difficult to stop Black's ...d5, White's structure is ugly, and the endgame favors Black thanks to the bishop pair. }
