{ This doesn't lose material thanks to  15.Qxg4  Rxb1+  . } 15. Qxg4 Rxb1+ 16.
Ke2 Rxh1
{ In a game, I'd think I'm winning with Black, but Stockfish manages to save. }
17. Bb5 O-O 18. Bxc6 Bh4 { Trying to trade queens. } 19. g3 Qg5
{ Black sacrifices the bishop to coordinate the rook and queen against the opponent's king. }
