17. Be2 Bxd5 18. exd5 g6 { Black slowly improves the position. } 19. Bxa6 Qf5
20. O-O e4 { Attacking b2. } 21. Qe2 Rfe8
{ White's extra pawn is doubled, and b5 is not going anywhere. Black will put a rook on e5 and redeploy the bishop to b6 via d8. }
