14. Qf3 { GM Shirov's pick. } 14... Be6
{ Black's plan differs from the lines we saw till now: ...Be7, ...Be6, ...Qd7, ...Bd8, ...Ne7. The aim is the same: eliminate the opponent's most active piece. }
15. Nce3 Qd7 { This variation transposes to 14.Nce3. } *

