16. Be2 Be6 { Played by GM Gelfand against GM Lagarde in 2021. } 17. Rd1 a5
{ 17...Rb8  18.Qg3  a5  19.Rg1  Bxd5  20.exd5  Bf4  21.Qf3  b3  22.axb3  Nb4  23.Nxb4  Rxb4  24.c5  dxc5  25.Bc4  Qd6  26.Qe4  Rfb8  27.Qf5  a4  28.Qe6+  Qxe6  29.dxe6  Kf8  30.Rd7  Rxc4  31.bxc4  Rxb2  32.Kf1  a3  33.Kg2  Be3  34.Kf3  Bd4  35.Ke4  a2  36.Ra7  Rb1  37.Rg3  a1=Q  38.Rf7+  Ke8  39.g5  Re1+  40.Kd5  Qa8+  41.Kd6  Qa6+  42.Kd5  Qa8+  43.Kd6  Qd8+  44.Rd7  Qb6+  45.Kd5  Rd1  46.gxf6  Bxf2+  47.Ke4  Qb1+  48.Kf3  Qf5+  49.Ke2  Rxd7  50.Rxg7  Rxg7  51.fxg7  Qg6  0-1 Lagarde-Gelfand, Biel blitz 2021. }
