1... Nxd5 2. Qxd5
{ 2.Nxd6+  Bxd6  @@StartBracket@@  2...Qxd6  3.Qxd5  Qxd5  4.Bxd5  Rxc2  5.Bxb7  a5  , Black remains with an active rook on the second rank.@@EndBracket@@ @@StartFEN@@2r1k2r/1pqb1ppp/p2b4/3np3/P7/1B2BP2/1PP3PP/R2Q1RK1 w k - 0 3@@EndFEN@@  3.Qxd5  Be6  transposes to the main line. }
2... Be6 3. Nxd6+
